{"content":[{"key":"header","data":{"content":"零、准备知识阶段","level":1},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><a href=\"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E6%98%BE%E5%8D%A1%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020\">显卡驱动</a></span><span>、</span><span>CUDA</span><span>、cuDNN之间联系以及安装配置</span>","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"在配置PyTorch的过程中，显卡驱动、CUDA、cuDNN三者之间的关系、作用以及在众多版本中如何搭配一直困扰着我。虽然网上资料很多，但各说其词，即使最终迈过种种坑成功运行，但脑子里还是一团乱麻。所以回过头来看NVIDIA的官方文档，一方面记录配置过程防止遗忘，另一方面也希望能够帮助有和我一样困惑的童鞋。本人能力有限，如有不妥之处，希望批评指正。"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>显卡</span><span>驱动、</span><span>CUDA</span><span>、cuDNN介绍</span>","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><strong>显卡</strong></span><span><strong>驱动</strong></span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>显卡</span><span>驱动是封装成软件的程序，硬件厂商根据</span><span>操作系统</span><span>编写的配置文件。安装成功后成为了操作系统中的一小块代码，它是硬件所对应的软件，有了它，计算机就可以与显卡进行通信，驱使其工作。如果没有显卡驱动，显卡就无法工作。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><strong>CUDA</strong></span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"官网introduction：其是由NVIDIA发明的并行计算平台以及编程模型，它可以显著的提高GPU的计算性能。官网introduction链接：https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/cuda-installation-guide-microsoft-windows/index.html"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><strong>cuDNN</strong></span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"官网综述：NVIDIA的cuDNN是针对深度神经网络计算的一个GPU加速库，为标准例程提供了高度优化的实现，比如向前、向后卷积，池化，规范化和激活层。其是NVIDIA Deep Learning SDK的一部分。官网综述链接：https://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/sdk/cudnn-install/有一个比喻能够更形象的说明CUDA、cuDNN两者的关系：CUDA看作是一个工作台，上面配有很多工具，如锤子、螺丝刀等。cuDNN是基于CUDA的深度学习GPU加速库，有了它才能在GPU上完成深度学习的计算。它就相当于工作的工具，比如它就是个扳手。但是CUDA这个工作台买来的时候，并没有送扳手。想要在CUDA上运行深度神经网络，就要安装cuDNN，就像你想要拧个螺帽就要把扳手买回来。这样才能使GPU进行深度神经网络的工作，工作速度相较CPU快很多。比喻出自：https://www.jianshu.com/p/622f47f94784<br>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"二、显卡驱动+CUD+cuDNN安装以及版本选择说明","level":1},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"2.1 显卡驱动安装（一般自己电脑都已经安装好了的）","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span><strong>已经安装</strong></span><span><strong>显卡</strong></span><span><strong>驱动进行如下步骤：</strong></span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>cuda</span><span>的版本一定要根据你自己的显卡型号来决定，所以这里记一下自己显卡驱动的版本</span><span>先右键桌面点击英伟达控制面板</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"url":"https://rqh3nmk4yk3.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=OGE2OTc0NjdiODkwMjNiNTFjMWI1YzQ2Mjg1ODdhOGVfMTB4SFR3R0QxV3lTQlJKTGRhRmo2WkRBTVNUcDlXUXhfVG9rZW46SDM5QWJMQW10b0NJaWp4RlZQZmNjU3VDbm5nXzE3MDY5Mjc1OTk6MTcwNjkzMTE5OV9WNA"},"caption":"","withCaption":true},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>点击左下角系统信息</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"url":"https://rqh3nmk4yk3.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=ZjVlYTY1MWU1MTRkNjA3M2ZjMzA2NGNhNmM4NjdlNTlfMEZHc1kwblBGOENGTzVQMElYbk5DQWZYVlFZUUlRTzlfVG9rZW46TnZQSmJJWkF0b0hnUjl4MDg1OGNwTWhrbmpmXzE3MDY5Mjc1OTk6MTcwNjkzMTE5OV9WNA"},"caption":"","withCaption":true},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>查看你的驱动程序版本（要记住了，一会就根据这个来选择</span><span>cuda</span><span>的版本）</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"url":"https://rqh3nmk4yk3.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=ODg0ZTlkMmIwNGI3MGQ0ZjU5OThiOTg4M2JlNzQ5ZWFfdWlMd2JEU0U5N2JvMFoxOFNVNlZQRE9qSnFOa0xBS3pfVG9rZW46UXVzZmJSNkxjb2lWNjZ4U3dTaGNvMlpIblVDXzE3MDY5Mjc1OTk6MTcwNjkzMTE5OV9WNA"},"caption":"","withCaption":true},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>看一下自己的驱动版本符合哪些</span><span>cuda</span><span>版本，你可以使用所有低于你驱动程序版本的cudatoolkit</span>比如我显卡驱动是5.46.12，那么我可以下载最新的